        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks CD for "Climbing plants" [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">4861</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Encloses sketch of a climbing French bean.</p>
            <p>Tells of a row of non-climbing haricot beans that in good season put out slender climbing shoots.</p>
            <p>He has the peach almond in fruit this season.</p>
